{"tid":1105592,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點解住公屋都話冇父幹上唔到車？","createTime":"2019-04-14T04:32:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-14T06:37:17.000Z","uid":171277,"like":8,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"b31cd23d13e34106fe10c93d367d021509ee67f5","tid":1105592,"uid":171277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T04:32:27.000Z","msg":"每個月既公屋租金同普遍家庭供樓既錢比起碼差1皮以上<br />\n<br />\n加埋可以申請埋政府d資助津貼<br />\n<br />\n讀書學費又平d 甚至1蚊都唔洗比<br />\n<br />\n屋企每個月慳番咁多錢，咁都話冇父幹？<br />\n用晒黎買iphone去旅行影相貼ig post出走文咋掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申<br />\n屋企本身供緊樓，根本唔會有多餘錢幫自己<br />\n<br />\n自己一畢業已欠緊政府十幾萬學費<br />\n<br />\n份工夠洗唔夠儲，1份工唔夠就放假做第2份，第2份唔夠就做埋第3份，fg果陣放工做埋第4份<br />\n<br />\n我身邊好多屋企有樓既朋友其實都係咁<br />\n<br />\n睇唔過眼d公屋仔日日叫春呻窮冇父幹<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cfd27a1ebbc69a4621d26a2f8089c8c8ee3ca69","tid":1105592,"uid":37746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T04:33:26.000Z","msg":"公屋先係人生贏家"},{"pid":"6cca4a1e95cbe070f5c427b5a5df67b0d03fe652","tid":1105592,"uid":29167,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T04:34:21.000Z","msg":"其實真係住公屋已經解決咗交租問題<br />\n儲錢真係易咗好多 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過啲公屋仔硬係要買貴嘢食好嘢成日去旅行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n邊有得怨"},{"pid":"c9a005e304b9e0284f4e5abc34dd194c8e975f36","tid":1105592,"uid":171277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9cfd27a1ebbc69a4621d26a2f8089c8c8ee3ca69","tid":1105592,"uid":37746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T04:33:26.000Z","msg":"公屋先係人生贏家"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T04:35:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 公屋仔成日話自己點慘點慘 轉頭渣部車出黎<br />\n<br />\n我就日日迫地鐵狗巴"},{"pid":"e6a6fe6542bb9e07b9fef0f1e5c9e06d11eed5f7","tid":1105592,"uid":